creator: Marietta Holley
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems by Marietta Holley.
Read in English by Ian King; Denver Grey; Sandra Schmit; Julia Niedermaier; DomBombadil; Sarah Jennings; NoelBadrian; Rosslyn Carlyle; Gemma L Myers; Larry Wilson; Kristin Gjerløw; Bruno Goh Luse; Lynne Thompson; Diana Schmidt; Renkotsu; Amy Gramour; Newgatenovelist; Peter Yearsley; Ezwa
This is a collection of poems by Marietta Holley, better known as Josiah Allen's Wife. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
